column5: i went two nights going 2 for 3 and 2 for 2 on walleye strikes.  one was too big the rest were right on the slot all fish taken on a bait that rocks
awesome nice fish, will definitely be good eats
Great looking fish.Perfect eatin size too I use a rockin' Bait too. Probably the same as yours
Nice eyes. You have to fillet them though  .
nice catch...  there are lots of areas around here for off-shore walleye at night... there are starting to load up with fish also...  after daylight savings goes back... thats gunna be fun...
Good fishing Kwan! I thought I knew you from some where, I was the guy who threw your TCard at AC
